data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING MONEY TOWARD BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS!!! Brightwater is the newest community in North Fort Myers - it is built around the upcoming six-acre freshwater lagoon surrounded by sandy beaches with swim-up bars, cabana cove, and water slides with highspeed internet throughout the community at 200mbps, a dog park, walking trails through the woods, sidewalks, gated access, and more of the little things you expect. This home is three bedrooms and two bathrooms with a split floorplan, a great room with all of the living spaces flowing together. The master suite has a stand-alone shower and separate room for the toilet - privacy at its finest! The master suite also has a walk-in closet outside the bathroom and another closet within the bathroom. The laundry room is inside and has its own closable door, not one of those tiny pass-thru’s to the garage! The patio is covered with extra pavers extended into the backyard with peaceful lake views - check the exterior and drone photos to see the view. The home was just extensively cleaned and re-painted.  The community's walking trails are really great to get outside but stay close to home.
